	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mi venerande Bullingere, charissime frater, ego semper erga omnes, quos mihi commendas, officium fecero<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName>Blarer</persName> hatte kurz zuvor auf Bullingers Empfehlung <persName>Konrad Lüthard</persName> berufen, vgl. oben <ref target="file10611">Nr. 573</ref>, 2-4.</note>, modo unum hoc a te impetrem, ut ne succenseas, quod rarissime quicquam ad te perscribo; nam sic discerpor etiam in<pb type="edition" next="207"/> sexcenta<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">unzählige (<bibl>Georges</bibl> II 2636).</note> negocia, ut nihil possim ad amicos.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Erit brevi forte, ut ocii plusculum adfulgeat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale et commenda me, ut facis, Christo.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta <persName>Pellicanum</persName>, <persName>Theodorum</persName><note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName>Theodor Bibliander</persName>.</note>, <persName ref="p2305">Leonem</persName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="p6796">Leo Jud</persName>.</note> et reliquos omnes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName>Tubingę</placeName>, 26. aprilis anno 1535.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vere tuus Ambros[ius] Bl[arer].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. Heinricho Bullingero, Tiguricen[sium] episcopo, domino et fratri multum in Christo venerando.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
